            </p>
            <ul class="mt-6 space-y-3">
              <li class="flex gap-3 items-start">
                <svg
                  class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  ><path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg
                >
                <span class="text-gray-600"
                  >Morbi viverra dui mi arcu sed. Tellus semper adipiscing
                  suspendisse semper morbi.</span
                >
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-3 items-start">
                <svg
                  class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  ><path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg
                >
                <span class="text-gray-600"
                  >Sit quis amet rutrum tellus ullamcorper ultricies libero
                  dolor eget.</span
                >
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-3 items-start">
                <svg
                  class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  ><path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
